# ask service broker who can respond to specified service requests
# @HELP signal <host>  provider <service>			# list hosts providing <service>
# @HELP signal <host>  provider <service1> <service2> ... 	# list hosts providing <service1>, <service2> ...
# transparently queries servicebroker. translates to    signal <servicebroker> provider <services>

signal @servicebroker servicebroker provider "$@"

# optimisiation potential here. see service_delegate.
# will probably drop these completely, and instead of:
#           signal localhost provider service
# go to
#           signal @serviceprovider provider service
